structurednavigation-desc: Describes the purpose of the StructuredNavigation extension
structurednavigation-separator-symbol: Defines the symbol/character that should be used for separating each link in a navigation.
structurednavigation-reserved-username: Defines the username that's reserved by this extension for doing automated tasks.
structurednavigation-view-navigation-not: The title shown for the empty state screen when a user visits a navigation that doesn't exist yet.
The summary shown for the empty state screen when a user visits a navigation that doesn't exist yet.
The button label shown on the empty state screen when a user visits a navigation that doesn't exist yet.
structurednavigation-copy-label: Label for the text input field that allows copying the embed code to the cliboard.
structurednavigation-copy-state-fail: A stateful message shown when copying the code to clipboard failed.
structurednavigation-copy-state-success: A stateful message shown when copying the code to clipboard was successful.
